node.text:
When I started #4BarFriday in 2013, I always wanted to create a series highlighting all the best MCs in the community. Every Friday through October 2021, I’ll be dropping episodes highlighting the stories of the best MCs in my #4BarFriday community. Next up is Waukegan, Illinois native @patentpendin. Part 2 of @patentpendin’s story drops next Friday. 

Follow @4barfriday to be a part of the movement.

When I started #4BarFriday in 2013, I always wanted to create a series highlighting all the best MCs in the community. Every Friday through October 2021, I’ll be dropping episodes highlighting the stories of the best MCs in my #4BarFriday community. Next up is Waukegan, Illinois native @patentpendin. Part 2 of @patentpendin’s story drops next Friday. 

Follow @4barfriday to be a part of the movement.
